==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tigrine
<hw>Ti"grine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tigrinus</ets>, fr. <ets>tigris</ets> a tiger.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Of or pertaining to a tiger; like a tiger.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Resembling the tiger in color;
<as>as, the <ex>tigrine</ex> cat (<spn>Felis tigrina</spn>) of South
America</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tigrish</ent>⟦br⟧
